data.description: Duckwood is a fabulous adult community in Stuart with 140 single family homes and is offering this amazing 1847 SF home their largest floor plan available!  Beautiful stone fireplace is the centerpiece of the living room which is open to the dining area and the Florida Room which has a lovely view of the rear yard.  The kitchen has plenty of counter space and cabinets open to the dining area.  There are 3 generous bedrooms with large closets and 2 full baths.  The beautiful clubhouse, pool, library and shuffleboard courts are right around the corner. You're never far away from the action with dozens of shops and restaurants close by including parks and beaches.  2 Semi private golf courses are a stones throw as well as Manatee Pocket and Port Salerno #ComeJoinUs
